<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>CERTIFICATE OF LIABILITY INSURANCE</title>
<style>
  body { font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1.4; max-width: 750px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 30px; color: #000; }
  h1 { font-size: 14pt; text-align: center; border: 2px solid #000; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .section { border: 1px solid #000; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .section-title { font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  td { padding: 3px 5px; vertical-align: top; }
  .label { font-weight: bold; width: 35%; }
  .disclaimer { font-size: 8pt; margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>CERTIFICATE OF LIABILITY INSURANCE</h1>

<div class="section">
  <div class="section-title">PRODUCER</div>
  <table>
    <tr><td class="label">Producer Name:</td><td>{{ producer_name }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="label">Address:</td><td>{{ producer_address }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="label">Contact:</td><td>{{ producer_contact }}</td></tr>
  </table>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="section-title">INSURED</div>
  <table>
    <tr><td class="label">Named Insured:</td><td>{{ named_insured }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="label">Address:</td><td>{{ insured_address }}</td></tr>
  </table>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="section-title">COVERAGES</div>
  {{ coverages }}
</div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="section-title">CERTIFICATE HOLDER</div>
  <table>
    <tr><td class="label">Name:</td><td>{{ certificate_holder }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="label">Address:</td><td>{{ holder_address }}</td></tr>
  </table>
</div>

<p class="disclaimer">
  THIS CERTIFICATE IS ISSUED AS A MATTER OF INFORMATION ONLY AND CONFERS NO RIGHTS UPON THE CERTIFICATE HOLDER.
  THIS CERTIFICATE DOES NOT AFFIRMATIVELY OR NEGATIVELY AMEND, EXTEND OR ALTER THE COVERAGE AFFORDED BY THE POLICIES BELOW.
</p>
</body>
</html>
